---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";

const pageTitle = "About";
---

<BaseLayout pageTitle={pageTitle}>
    <div class="">
        <h1 class="font-mono font-bold text-3xl md:text-4xl">About</h1>
        <div class="mt-12">
            <p class="">Hi, how are you? I hope you are fine!</p>
            <p class="mt-3">
                My name is <span class="font-mono text-violet-700"
                    >Muhammad Hafid Khoirul</span
                >, people usually call me
                <span class="font-mono text-violet-700">Hafid</span>.
            </p>
            <p class="mt-3">
                I'm a software developer based in Bogor, Indonesia, currently
                working as a backend engineer at <a
                    class="font-mono text-violet-700 hover:text-violet-800 border-b border-violet-700"
                    href="https://www.qontak.com"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="norefferer">Qontak</a
                >. I have been working as a backend engineer since I graduated
                from Brawijaya University in 2020 with computer engineer major.
                So, it's been 4 years, time does flies fast.
            </p>
            <p class="mt-3">
                I'm focused on backend technology right now. Mainly use Ruby on
                Rails at the moment, tried a lot of things, Go, Phoenix, NestJs,
                etc, love them. Beside web development, I also interested in
                other fields like computer vision and IoT. Doing small projects
                in my spare time. My thesis was about computer vision by the
                way, you can read <a
                    class="font-mono text-violet-700 hover:text-violet-800 border-b border-violet-700"
                    href="https://j-ptiik.ub.ac.id/index.php/j-ptiik/article/view/7129"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="norefferer">here</a
                >.
            </p>
            <p class="mt-3">
                I made this site to be my portfolio and blog. My writing skill
                needs a lot of practices... That's why I'm going to share
                everything I want here. This will work also as my note, dont't
                forget everything after you learn something, take notes!
            </p>
            <p class="mt-3">
                Finally, thank you for visiting this site, means a lot.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</BaseLayout>
